svg.script:
<![CDATA[
(function() {
    const svg = document.querySelector('svg');
    const dots = Array.from(svg.querySelectorAll('.dot'));

    svg.addEventListener('mousemove', (e) => {
        const pt = svg.createSVGPoint();
        pt.x = e.clientX;
        pt.y = e.clientY;
        const cursor = pt.matrixTransform(svg.getScreenCTM().inverse());

        dots.forEach(dot => {
            const cx = parseFloat(dot.getAttribute('cx'));
            const cy = parseFloat(dot.getAttribute('cy'));
            const dx = cx - cursor.x;
            const dy = cy - cursor.y;
            const dist = Math.sqrt(dx * dx + dy * dy);
            const scale = Math.max(1, 3 - dist / 80);

            dot.setAttribute('transform', `translate(${cx},${cy}) scale(${scale}) translate(${-cx},${-cy})`);
            dot.style.transition = 'transform 0.2s ease';
        });
    });

    svg.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
        dots.forEach(dot => {
            const cx = parseFloat(dot.getAttribute('cx'));
            const cy = parseFloat(dot.getAttribute('cy'));
            dot.setAttribute('transform', `translate(${cx},${cy}) scale(1) translate(${-cx},${-cy})`);
        });
    });
})();
]]>
